title: Promo Only Mainstream Club March 1993
description:
This is the oldest Promo Only Mainstream Club that I have.  Given that, it is yet another collectors item for me.  You can&#039;t go wrong with Whitney&#039;s LONG version of "I&#039;m Every Woman" or a "new" remix of Baltimora&#039;s "Tarzan Boy".  I wish I had the picture of the CD but I do not, alas.  

Mainstream club was very different in March 1993, even though it was only 15 years ago.  

Enjoy!!
